snippet.title: The Amazing Eternals: Make Your Move
snippet.description:
Make your move. Join The Amazing Eternals -- where each move transports you into an epic battle, blending first-person action and deck-building strategy for an all new type of FREE team-based shooter.
Become a Founder on August 29 and join in our development quest! amazingeternals.com
